data.description: Enjoy the ease of one-floor living in this beautiful 4 bed, 3 full bath ranch w nearly ~3,000 sqft of living space! The home also boasts a convenient in-law suite + in-ground pool for those warm weather days ahead! Formal living and dining rooms. Spacious light-filled family room w fireplace, cathedral ceiling + skylights! Kitchen w granite countertops, classic subway tile backsplash, + cabinet space galore w adjoining breakfast area - all kitchen appliances stay! Large owner's suite w attached bath ft double vanity, soaking tub + shower! In-law suite boasts bedroom, attached flex room w walkout + easy access to hallway bath. Two addl large bedrooms. The backyard is an entertainer's dream - fully-enclosed privacy fence, in-ground pool w covered patio, fire pit area. Mechanical updates - pool pump ('23), pool filter ('22), water heather ('22), HVAC ('15). No HOA! Imagine yourself poolside this summer in your new backyard! Don't delay - this home is the one you've been looking for!
